function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	tSnakes = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Bog_SnakeAltarSnakes")
	
	for i, ActorID in ipairs(tSnakes) do
	
		Hydra.ActorEnable(ActorID)
	
	end
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idLorath, 0.75)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, idLorathRunLoc_01, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleRunLoc_01, "NPC_Run", true)
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)

	Hydra.QActorSheath(idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, idLorathRunLoc_02, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorath, idLorathRunLoc_02, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_Lorath_Incense, idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimOneShot(idLorath, "AnimKey_ItemGive_Phased")
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idLorath, "Moved")
	
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idNeyrelle, 0.5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleRunLoc_02, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleRunLoc_02, true)
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.ActorEnable(idIncenseBowlSwitch)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idIncenseBowlEmpty)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	-- Play IGC
	CampaignForcedPartyGatherPlayIGC(conv_HSS, idActorPlayer)

	-- Disable the Bowl
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idActorGizmo)
end
